{"tid":2086475,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"隔幾日又有死亡意外","createTime":"2020-06-30T09:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T09:52:02.000Z","uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a9cf8c2f0f75c65f9a15a44d88e4c38e7b710585","tid":2086475,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"機場三跑再次發生奪命意外。下午2時許，兩名非華裔工人於機場三跑工程地盤工作，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其間疑遭鋼纜擊中，二人走避不及受傷</strong></span>，其中年約30歲的男子頭部重創，昏迷不醒，另一人則手腳受傷。工友發現後立即報警，水警輪到場將二人載走送至海天碼頭，之後再由救護車轉送北大嶼山醫院，不過<span style=\"color: red;\">頭部重傷的工人送院搶救後不治</span>，而另一人則仍在醫院留醫中，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n機場三跑地盤曾發生奪命意外，<span style=\"color: red;\">去年8月12日</span>，一名38歲姓鍾工人駕駛推土機時懷疑操作失控，連人帶推土機一同墮海，經救起送院搶救後證實不治，遺下妻子及三名子女。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200630&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=61114289\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200630%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D61114289&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2FwRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=8ce71e13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200630%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D61114289&h=5a5ae702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200630&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=61114289</a>"},{"pid":"f095410f91f3012f3a4c989a228978f07bc895ca","tid":2086475,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bff0a19b2d5331d5094ca76c694409b92581c6","tid":2086475,"uid":19817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:52:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2086300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span styl